item.title: The Power of Belief - How Mindset Fuels Your Potential
item.description: Let me tell you a story about Emma because I think you can learn something to help you create your ideal business and ideal life. Emma had dreamed of starting her own baking business since she was 10 years old, mixing cupcakes in her mom's kitchen. After college, she decided it was time.
